Package: deconvML
Type: Package
Title: A single cell data resource
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Alicia", "Gómez Pascual", email = "alicia.gomez1@um.es", 
    role = c("aut", "cre")), person("Juan A.", "Botía Blaya", role = "aut"))
Description: A single cell data resource. It consists of a catalog through which the user can 
    answer questions about their dataset in relation to the number of genes and cells that 
    compose it, the different tissues and cell types included, and the methods available to 
    estimate the active genes. Finally, it estimates the active genes for a certain cell type 
    included in a tissue for a specific method and dataset.
